Từ điển Anh - Việt
◘['neibəli]
 ■như neighbourly

Kết hợp từ & Cấu trúc câu
neighborly
adj.AE
BEspelling: neighbourly neighborly to + inf. (it was neighborly of you to do that)

sentences.en: She was very neighborly.
